'''''Jungle Flutes''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Propaganda/Legends|propaganda]] [[Holodrama/Legends|holodrama]] that starred the young holofilm celebrity, [[Garik Loran]]. It was badly received by many [[Lorrdian/Legends|Lorrdian]] and [[Argazdan/Legends|Argazdan]] viewers at the [[Qatamer]] [[Performance Square]] due to its blatantly pro-Imperial stance. Posters of the film were torn apart by several irate Lorrdians.<ref name="XWING">''[[X-Wing: Wraith Squadron]]''</ref>

